  "3072620": {
    "name": "R-Type Delta: HD Boosted",
    "steam_appid": 3072620,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072620/extras/4b6eaa2e7736e80e14c7206c7073dac5.poster.avif?t=1770718845\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072620/extras/4b6eaa2e7736e80e14c7206c7073dac5.webm?t=1770718845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072620/extras/4b6eaa2e7736e80e14c7206c7073dac5.mp4?t=1770718845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■重生的「R」奇点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >革新了《R-TYPE》系列的名作《R-TYPE DELTA》在现行机种上复活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >历经27年，携带众多新要素，以“HD Boosted”之姿新生，再次投入战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072620/extras/7c38fc2860294530b03dcb96b2e4e169.poster.avif?t=1770718845\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072620/extras/7c38fc2860294530b03dcb96b2e4e169.webm?t=1770718845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072620/extras/7c38fc2860294530b03dcb96b2e4e169.mp4?t=1770718845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >公元2163年，跨次元战机R9-Arrowhead完成了摧毁Bydo帝国核心的任务，并返回位于地球卫星轨道上的宇宙要塞“Aegis”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类虽一度沉浸在安堵之中，但翌年地表观测到不明坠落物，各地相继发生异常现象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更有被封印的歼灭兵器「Moritz-G」出现在亚洲某市街地，由于自我防御系统失控而成为威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迎击部队陷入苦战，最终试作机 R9 Delta 奋然出击——。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072620/extras/3fc37df6e88aec521f4b93aec65c7766.poster.avif?t=1770718845\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072620/extras/3fc37df6e88aec521f4b93aec65c7766.webm?t=1770718845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072620/extras/3fc37df6e88aec521f4b93aec65c7766.mp4?t=1770718845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■善用 Force＆Dose 系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗的关键，也是系列的核心，就是“Force”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它是一种既能对敌人造成伤害，又能吸收子弹的生命体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得激光结晶后可强化至三个等级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据情况灵活运用 Force 的合体与分离来推进战斗吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >初始状态下可以选择三种具备不同性质和攻击方式的机体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外，通过使用 Force 摧毁或吸收敌人和敌弹，可以积累能量的「Dose 系统」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在最大蓄力时，攻击力会提升，并且 Force 的接触范围会扩大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >释放后即可发动全屏攻击「Δ-Weapon」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072620/extras/d2f839c1bf71848aa532a2da13e49df1.poster.avif?t=1770718845\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072620/extras/d2f839c1bf71848aa532a2da13e49df1.webm?t=1770718845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072620/extras/d2f839c1bf71848aa532a2da13e49df1.mp4?t=1770718845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■以高清图像重生的「R」世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由多边形描绘的游戏画面，进化为支持HD画幅的高清视觉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >钢铁的厚重感、敌生命体的恐怖，以及光芒的耀眼，都能直接传达，把玩家带入前所未有的 R-TYPE 世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072620/extras/aaf1cf9a124da374b00da956bda712bd.poster.avif?t=1770718845\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072620/extras/aaf1cf9a124da374b00da956bda712bd.webm?t=1770718845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072620/extras/aaf1cf9a124da374b00da956bda712bd.mp4?t=1770718845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
